    <h1>Privacy Policy for Guardian Angel</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 5, 2026</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Guardian Angel ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect the following information that you provide directly:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Your age</li>
        <li>Your location (city or country)</li>
        <li>Personal reflections and concerns you choose to share</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Personalize your spiritual guidance and daily wisdom</li>
        <li>Provide relevant Bible verses and messages</li>
        <li>Maintain your conversation history within the app</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>All your personal data is stored locally on your device</li>
        <li>We do not store your data on external servers</li>
        <li>Your conversation history remains on your device only</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use Google's Gemini AI API to generate personalized spiritual guidance. When you receive daily wisdom or chat with the app:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your information (name, age, location, and what's on your heart) is sent to Google's Gemini API</li>
        <li>This data is used only to generate personalized responses</li>
        <li>Google's privacy policy applies to this data processing: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>We Do Not:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Sell your personal information</li>
        <li>Share your data with third parties (except Gemini API as described above)</li>
        <li>Track your activity outside the app</li>
        <li>Collect any data beyond what you explicitly provide</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
    <p>You can delete your data at any time by:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Using the "Clear" button in the app to delete your conversation history</li>
        <li>Deleting the app from your device (this removes all locally stored data)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This app is intended for users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13 without parental consent.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last updated" date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <strong>[theodorsandub@gmail.com]</strong></p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the data we have about you</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of data collection by not using the app</li>
    </ul>
</body>
